OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FJudge described sexual     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpredator as 'Jack the lad' 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A part-time judge who described a      
OL,6, convicted sex offender as "Jack the    
OL,7, lad" during sentencing has been        
OL,8, criticised by a Court of Appeal judge. 
OL,10,FRecorder John Hardy used the phrase    
OL,11,Fwhen sentencing Aaron Hewson, 33, for  
OL,12,Fthree sexual assaults at Norwich Crown 
OL,13,FCourt in April.                        
OL,15,FLady Justice Macur, who oversaw an     
OL,16,Fappeal hearing on Thursday, said she   
OL,17,F"deplored" Recorder Hardy's indication.
OL,19,FHewson's sentence was increased after  
OL,20,Fbeing considered unduly lenient.       
